<p><img src="https://static.raymondcamden.com/images/2016/12/intl5.png" alt="Demo"></p>
<p>For comparison, here is the home page with English set as my language:</p>
<p><img src="https://static.raymondcamden.com/images/2016/12/intl2.png" alt="Demo"></p>
